{
  "chapter": 25,
  "chapter_summary": "第25回\"舍我其谁\"，江南十剑中的单亦飞、柳枯竹，以及富贵神仙手、老和尚等人齐聚大老板处，要铲除天尊在此地的恶势力。战斗中大老板被双剑穿喉毙命，竹叶青被老和尚击倒。阿吉出手夺下柳枯竹的剑救下小弟，老和尚揭露小弟是天尊派来的密使，大老板和竹叶青只是他的傀儡。阿吉为救小弟，说出自己就是翠云峰绿水湖神剑山庄的三少爷谢晓峰——天下无双的剑客。然而小弟趁谢晓峰不备，用七十二小擒拿手扣住他的脉门，单亦飞趁机以木脚暗剑刺伤谢晓峰。谢晓峰忍痛反击，削断富贵神仙手的十指，刺倒柳枯竹，将小弟送出门外后只身挡住追兵。竹叶青苏醒后暗示夫人手下有能与谢晓峰匹敌的剑客——燕十三。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "贵客尊姓？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 3,
      "line_end": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_dan_yi_fei",
      "text": "贵客莫非还有三位朋友要来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 7,
      "line_end": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dan_yi_fei",
      "speaker_name": "独臂人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哼。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 9,
      "line_end": 9
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_er",
      "speaker_name": "仇二",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好得很，想不到连你也来了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 29,
      "line_end": 29
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老和尚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我不来谁来？我不入地狱谁入地狱？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 31,
      "line_end": 31
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": "char_lao_he_shang",
      "text": "幸好这里不是地狱，大师既然到了这里，也就不必再受那十方苦难。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 39,
      "line_end": 39
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老和尚",
      "listener": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "text": "这里不是地狱，哪里是地狱？我不来受苦，谁来受苦？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 41,
      "line_end": 41
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": "char_lao_he_shang",
      "text": "到了这里，大师还要受什么苦？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 45,
      "line_end": 45
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老和尚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "降魔也苦，杀人也苦。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 47,
      "line_end": 47
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": "char_lao_he_shang",
      "text": "大师也杀人？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 49,
      "line_end": 49
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老和尚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我不杀人谁杀人？不杀人又何必入地狱？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 51,
      "line_end": 51
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dan_yi_fei",
      "speaker_name": "独臂人",
      "listener": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "text": "你知道我是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 55,
      "line_end": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dan_yi_fei",
      "speaker_name": "单亦飞",
      "listener": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "text": "你应该知道我是谁的，像我这样只有单眼、单手、单腿的人，却能用双剑的只怕还没有几个。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 61,
      "line_end": 61
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": "char_dan_yi_fei",
      "text": "是单大侠！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 67,
      "line_end": 67
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dan_yi_fei",
      "speaker_name": "单亦飞",
      "listener": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "text": "不错，我就是单亦飞，我也是来杀人的。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 69,
      "line_end": 69
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ku_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "柳枯竹",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "还有我柳枯竹。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 73,
      "line_end": 73
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dan_yi_fei",
      "speaker_name": "单亦飞",
      "listener": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "text": "我们今天要来杀的是什么人，我不说想必你也知道！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 77,
      "line_end": 77
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": "char_dan_yi_fei",
      "text": "幸好各位要来杀的不是我。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老和尚",
      "listener": "char_a_ji",
      "text": "阁下好快的出手。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 111,
      "line_end": 111
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_ji",
      "speaker_name": "阿吉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我也会杀人。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 113,
      "line_end": 113
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老和尚",
      "listener": "char_a_ji",
      "text": "这件事和阁下有没有关系？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 115,
      "line_end": 115
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_ji",
      "speaker_name": "阿吉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 117,
      "line_end": 117
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老和尚",
      "listener": "char_a_ji",
      "text": "那么阁下何苦多管闲事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 119,
      "line_end": 119
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_ji",
      "speaker_name": "阿吉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为这个人和我有点关系。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 121,
      "line_end": 121
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老和尚",
      "listener": "char_a_ji",
      "text": "阁下若是一定要救他，只怕难得很。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 123,
      "line_end": 123
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_ji",
      "speaker_name": "阿吉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 125,
      "line_end": 125
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老和尚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为那双手。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 127,
      "line_end": 127
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老和尚",
      "listener": "char_a_ji",
      "text": "那就是'点石成金，点活成死'的富贵神仙搜魂手。阁下就算杀了柳枯竹，那位少年施主也必死无疑。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 131,
      "line_end": 131
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_ji",
      "speaker_name": "阿吉",
      "listener": "char_lao_he_shang",
      "text": "难道你们不惜以柳枯竹的一条命，换他的一条命？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 133,
      "line_end": 133
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老和尚",
      "listener": "char_a_ji",
      "text": "是的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 135,
      "line_end": 135
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_ji",
      "speaker_name": "阿吉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他只不过还是个孩子，你们为何一定要置他于死地？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 137,
      "line_end": 137
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老和尚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "孩子？他只不过是个孩子？像这样的孩子世上只怕还不多。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 139,
      "line_end": 139
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_ji",
      "speaker_name": "阿吉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他今年还不到十五。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 141,
      "line_end": 141
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老和尚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那么我们就绝不容他活到十六。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 143,
      "line_end": 143
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_ji",
      "speaker_name": "阿吉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 145,
      "line_end": 145
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老和尚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你知不知道'天尊'？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 149,
      "line_end": 149
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_ji",
      "speaker_name": "阿吉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "天尊？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 151,
      "line_end": 151
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老和尚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "天地无情。鬼神无眼。万物无能。壮民无知。生死无常。祸福无门。天地幽冥，唯我独尊。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 153,
      "line_end": 153
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_ji",
      "speaker_name": "阿吉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这是谁说的？好大的口气。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 155,
      "line_end": 155
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老和尚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这就是'天尊'开宗立派的祝文，连天地鬼神都没有被他们看在眼里，何况是人？他们的所作所为，也就可想而知了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 157,
      "line_end": 157
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_er",
      "speaker_name": "仇二",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他们势力的庞大，已不在昔年的青龙会之下，可惜江湖中偏偏还有我们这几个不信邪的人，偏偏要跟他们拼一拼。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 159,
      "line_end": 159
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dan_yi_fei",
      "speaker_name": "单亦飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所以江南十剑和仇二之间的一点私仇，已变得算不了什么，只要能消灭他们的恶势力，单某连头颅都可抛却，何况一点私仇而已！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 161,
      "line_end": 161
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_er",
      "speaker_name": "仇二",
      "listener": "char_a_ji",
      "text": "这地方的恶势力帮会，就是'天尊'属下的一股支流。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 163,
      "line_end": 163
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老和尚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们暂时还不可能铲除他们的根本，就只有先从小处着手！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 165,
      "line_end": 165
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_er",
      "speaker_name": "仇二",
      "listener": "char_a_ji",
      "text": "你要救的这孩子，就是'天尊'派到这里来的！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 167,
      "line_end": 167
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老和尚",
      "listener": "char_a_ji",
      "text": "天尊的命令，全都由他在暗中指挥操纵，大老板和竹叶青都只不过是他的傀儡而已。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 169,
      "line_end": 169
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老和尚",
      "listener": "char_a_ji",
      "text": "现在你总该已明白我们为何不能放过他。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 173,
      "line_end": 173
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老和尚",
      "listener": "char_a_ji",
      "text": "现在你既然已明白了，是不是还想救他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 179,
      "line_end": 179
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_ji",
      "speaker_name": "阿吉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是的。",
      "tone": "坚定",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 181,
      "line_end": 181
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_ji",
      "speaker_name": "阿吉",
      "listener": "char_lao_he_shang",
      "text": "他是不是天尊的首脑？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 187,
      "line_end": 187
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老和尚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "当然不是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 189,
      "line_end": 189
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_ji",
      "speaker_name": "阿吉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "天尊的首脑是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 191,
      "line_end": 191
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老和尚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "天尊的首脑，就叫做天尊。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 193,
      "line_end": 193
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_ji",
      "speaker_name": "阿吉",
      "listener": "char_lao_he_shang",
      "text": "若有人用天尊的一条命，来换这孩子的一条命，你们肯不肯？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 195,
      "line_end": 195
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老和尚",
      "listener": "char_a_ji",
      "text": "当然肯，只可惜就算我们肯，这交易也是一定做不成的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 197,
      "line_end": 197
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_ji",
      "speaker_name": "阿吉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 199,
      "line_end": 199
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老和尚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为没有人能杀天尊，没有人是他的对手。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 201,
      "line_end": 201
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老和尚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "也许还有一个人。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 205,
      "line_end": 205
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_ji",
      "speaker_name": "阿吉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 207,
      "line_end": 207
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老和尚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "三……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 209,
      "line_end": 209
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老和尚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只可惜这个人已不在人世了，说出来也无用！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 211,
      "line_end": 211
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_ji",
      "speaker_name": "阿吉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可是你说出来又有何妨？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 213,
      "line_end": 213
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老和尚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "天上地下，只有这么样独一无二的一个人，独一无二的一把剑，只有他的剑法，才真是独步千古，天下无双。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 217,
      "line_end": 217
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_ji",
      "speaker_name": "阿吉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你说的是……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 219,
      "line_end": 219
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老和尚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我说的是三少爷。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 221,
      "line_end": 221
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_ji",
      "speaker_name": "阿吉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哪一位三少爷？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 223,
      "line_end": 223
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老和尚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "翠云峰，绿水湖，神剑山庄的谢家三少爷谢晓峰。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 225,
      "line_end": 225
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_ji",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我就是谢晓峰！",
      "tone": "坚定",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 227,
      "line_end": 227
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老和尚",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你就是谢家的三少爷谢晓峰？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 251,
      "line_end": 251
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我就是。",
      "tone": "坚定",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 253,
      "line_end": 253
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老和尚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 259,
      "line_end": 259
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ku_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "柳枯竹",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为除了谢晓峰外，我实在想不出还有别人能在一招内夺下我的剑！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 261,
      "line_end": 261
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老和尚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 263,
      "line_end": 263
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "富贵神仙手",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你是不是忘了做一件事？忘了去谢谢三少爷的救命之恩？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 277,
      "line_end": 277
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_di",
      "speaker_name": "小弟",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你……你为什么要救我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 285,
      "line_end": 285
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ku_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "柳枯竹",
      "listener": "char_xiao_di",
      "text": "你疯了。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 327,
      "line_end": 327
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老和尚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "果然是天下无双的剑法，果然是天下无双的谢晓峰！",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 357,
      "line_end": 357
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "剑法确实是好的，天下无双则未必。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 359,
      "line_end": 359
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老和尚",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "叶先生的剑法当然也是好的，刚才为何不拔剑而起，与他一决胜负？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 363,
      "line_end": 363
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我比不上他。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 367,
      "line_end": 367
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老和尚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你知道有谁能比得上他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 369,
      "line_end": 369
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "至少还有一个人！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 371,
      "line_end": 371
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老和尚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "夫人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 373,
      "line_end": 373
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_lao_he_shang",
      "text": "你见过夫人出手？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 377,
      "line_end": 377
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老和尚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 379,
      "line_end": 379
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那只因夫人纵然要杀人，也用不着自己出手。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 381,
      "line_end": 381
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老和尚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有谁能替她出手，将谢晓峰置之于死地？",
